# Playwright MCP server logs
.playwright-mcp/

# ML artefacts — adapters, intermediate datasets, checkpoints.
# Ignore everything under data/ml/ EXCEPT the shipped Ubuntu-tuned
# pointer-accel and long-jump models (+ their training datasets).
# They're load-bearing for fast cursor homing on the default
# Ubuntu + redglass setup; users targeting other OSes or webcams
# follow the README runbook to add their own pointer_accel-vN /
# longjump-vN checkpoints alongside.
data/ml/*
!data/ml/checkpoints/
data/ml/checkpoints/*
!data/ml/checkpoints/pointer_accel-*/
!data/ml/checkpoints/longjump-*/
!data/ml/pointer_accel/
!data/ml/longjump/
*.safetensors
